\c 26
\s Rwiyo ruchaimbiwa panyika yaJudha
\p
\v 1 Nezuva iro rwiyo urwu ruchaimbiwa panyika yaJudha: Tine guta rakasimba; \add Mwari\add* achamisa ruponeso kuva masvingo nenhare.
\v 2 Zarurai masuwo, kuti rudzi rwakarurama rwunochengetedza chokwadi rwupinde.
\v 3 Ucha\add mu\add*chengeta parugare rwakakwana, fungwa dzake dzimire pamusoro pako, nokuti anovimba nemi.
\v 4 Vimbai naJehovha nekusingaperi, nokuti muna Ishe JEhovha mune dombo rekusingaperi.
\v 5 Nokuti anoderedza pasi vagari vepakakwirira, guta rakakwirira, anoriisa pakaderera, anoriisa pasi kusvika pavhu, anorisvitsa muguruva.
\v 6 Rutsoka rwucharitsikira-tsikira pasi, rutsoka rwemurombo, nhanho dzevanoshaiwa.
\p
\v 7 Nzira yevakarurama kururama; iwe wakarurama, unoyera gwara revakarurama.
\v 8 Zvirokwazvo, panzira yemitongo yenyu Jehovha, takakumirirai, chishuwo chemweya \add yedu\add* chiri pazita renyu nepachirangaridzo.
\v 9 Nemweya wangu ndakakushuvai usiku; uye neupenyu hwangu mukati mangu ndakakutsvakai kwazvo, nokuti mitongo yenyu painenge iri panyika, vagari vepanyika vachadzidza kururama.
\v 10 Wakaipa akawana nyasha haadzidzi kururama, munyika yakarurama achaita zvakaipa, uye haangaoni ukuru hwaJehovha.
\v 11 Jehovha, ruoko rwenyu rwakasimudzwa, havangaoni, \add asi\add* vachaona, vagonyara kushingaira kwenyu pamusoro pevanhu, kutsamwa kwemoto wevavengi venyu uchavapedza.
\p
\v 12 Jehovha muchatimisira rugare, nokuti nemwi makatiitira mabasa edu ese.
\v 13 Jehovha Mwari wedu, mamwe madzishe kunze kwenyu akange akatibata; asi ticharumbidza zita renyu tichibatsirwa nemwi moga.
\v 14 Vakafa havangararamizve, vaparara, havazomukizve; saka makasvika kwavari, mukavaparadza, nokugumisa kurangarirwa kwavo kwese.
\v 15 Mawanza rudzi, Jehovha, mawanza rudzi; makurumbira, makurisa miganho yese yenyika.
\v 16 Jehovha, vakakutsvakai panguva yokutambudzika; vakadurura munyengetero muchivaranga.
\v 17 Mukadzi ane pamuviri, asvika pedo pakusununguka, sezvaanorwadziwa achichema pakurwadziwa kwake, ndizvo zvatakange takaita pamberi penyu, Jehovha.
\v 18 Isu takange tava nepamuviri, takange tiri pakurwadziwa, takabereka zvinenge mhepo chete; hatina kuvigira nyika sununguro, uye vangagara panyika havana kuzvarwa.
\v 19 Vakafa venyu vachararama, zvitunha zvavo zvichamuka. Mukai, muimbe, imwi mugere muguruva; nokuti dova renyu rakaita sedova rechiedza; nyika ichabudisa vakafa.
\p
\v 20 Fambai vanhu vangu mupinde mumba yenyu yomukati, mupfige mikova yenyu shure kwenyu; muvande nguva diki, kusvikira kutsamwa kwapfuura.
\v 21 Nokuti tarira Jehovha anobuda panzvimbo yake kurova vagere panyika nokuda kwezvivi zvavo; nyikawo ichafukura ropa rayo, ikasazofukidzazve vakaurawa vayo.
